para_trans: Regarding disbursement of funds for Shabari Tribal Housing (Urban) Scheme in urban areas for this economic year:
Government Purification Card No: BUD-2024 / Q.No.08 / Ka-06
Madame Cama Road, Mahatma Rajguru Chowk
Read: - 1) Department of Finance, Government Circular No. 01.04.2024.
2) Department of Finance, Government Circular No. 15.07.2024.
3) Government Decision, Tribal Development Department, No. BUD-2024 / Q. 08 / Ka-06, D. 10.10.2024.

The Additional Commissioner (Tribal Development) under the Shabari Adivasi Gharakul Yojana (Urban) for the financial year 2024-25 has been appointed as the Project Officer, Integrated Tribal Development Project-wise, under his / her Subordinate No. 3 The funds have been disbursed as per the government decision here. In this Government Decision, in A.No.1, the Additional Commissioner (Tribal Development), Nashik, Subordinate Drawing and Distribution Officer and Project Officer, AAVP Nashik, "shall be read as Drawing and Distribution Officer and Project Officer, AAVP." This jashan purification sheet is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
